Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When you write the kanji "cherry blossom,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,do not use that slash on top of the right part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, in the old style kanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it has two "sea shell" characters\Nup on top of the right part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:47.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This person isn't Imai, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's Hokuto's lackey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Grr...
